
<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span12">
      
    <section class="brand">
      <header>
        <h1><a href="#">HackDash</a></h1>
      </header>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Ideas for a hackathon</h2>
        <p>Upload your project. Add colaborators. Inform status. Share your app.</p>

        {{#isLoggedIn}}
        <form>
          <p class="control-group">
            <input class="input-xlarge" id="domain" maxlength="10"
              placeholder="Hackathon domain Name (5-10 chars)" type="text">
            <label>(5-10 lowercase letters/numbers)</label>
          </p>

          <p>
            <input id="create-dashboard" class="btn btn-large btn-custom disabled" type="button" value="Create a Dashboard">
          </p>
        </form>
        {{else}}
        <p>
          <a class="btn btn-large btn-custom" href="/login">Log in to create a Hackathon</a>
        </p>
        {{/isLoggedIn}}
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span12">
    <div class="span6">
      <section class="block">
        <header>
          <h3>Find Projects</h3>
          <p>Search hackathon projects all over the world in one place.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="content span12">
          <p class="control-group">
            <input class="input-large search-box" id="search-projects"
              placeholder="name or description" type="text">
            <button class="btn btn-large btn-custom disabled search-btn" id="search-projects-btn">Search</button>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="span6">
      <section class="block">
        <header>
          <h3>Find Collections</h3>
          <p>Search and organize groups of dashboards with "Collections".</p>
        </header>

        <div class="content span12">
          <p class="control-group">
            <input class="input-large search-box" id="search-collections"
              placeholder="name or description" type="text">
            <button class="btn btn-large btn-custom disabled search-btn" id="search-collections-btn">Search</button>
            <button class="btn btn-large btn-custom disabled search-btn" id="create-collections-btn">Create</button>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span12">
    <section class="block">
      <header>
        <h3>About</h3>
      </header>

      <div class="content span11">
        <p>The HackDash was born by accident and by a need.
        We were looking for platform to track ideas through
        hackathons in the line to the Hacks/Hackers Media
        Party organized by @HacksHackersBA where hackers
        and journalists share ideas. We spread the idea
        through Twitter and that was the context of the
        HackDash born. @blejman had an idea and
        @danzajdband was interested in implement that idea.
        So we started building the app hoping we can get to
        the Buenos Aires media party with something that
        doesn't suck. The Media Party Hackathon day came
        followed by a grateful surprise. Not only the
        people liked the HackDash implementation but a
        couple of coders added the improvement of the
        HackDash as a Hackaton project. After the Media
        Party we realized that this small app is filling a
        real need. The Dashboard has been used now in
        several ways like Node.js Argentina meetup,
        HacksHackersBA, La Naci√≥n DataFest and
        HackasHackersCL (using it as a Wordpress theme).
        Now, the HackDash will be an standard for
        hackathons through the PinLatAm program, for news
        innovation in Latin America. Create your own
        hackathon.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

